# STEP 3 тАФ DD Path Graph

DD = Decision-to-Decision

DD path graph me:

* Sequential statements combine ho jate hain
* Sirf decision points important hote hain

---

## Decision Nodes

* Node 2 тЖТ if(A>0)
* Node 5 тЖТ if(C>10)

---

## DD Paths

```text
Start тЖТ 2 тЖТ 5 тЖТ End
```

Branches:

```text
2(T) тЖТ 5
2(F) тЖТ 5

5(T) тЖТ End
5(F) тЖТ End
```

